overview: Gala comedy festival featuring William Shatner, Adam Hills, Fiona O'Loughlin, Damon Wayans, Men in Coats, Dom Irrera, Lewis Black, Jimmy Carr, Danny Bhoy, Greg Proops, Spy Monkey, Colin Mochrie & Brad Sherwood, John Moloney, Jeremy Hotz, Amy G, Tommy Tiernan, Russell Peters, Sean Cullen, Frank Skinner, and "heaps more."
title: The International Comedy Festival - Montreal 2007
